    <item>
      <title>交易员无视中国对人民币的支持，导致人民币跌至一年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/china-s-yuan-falls-to-one-year-low-on-tariff-risk-dollar-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们无视中国支撑人民币的努力，导致人民币跌至一年来的最低点，原因是投资者押注中国经济增长乏力以及美国提高关税的风险，决策者将不得不进一步放松货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/china-s-yuan-falls-to-one-year-low-on-tariff-risk-dollar-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 01:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
